| 
| Meta-type representing the assignment statement, which associates a named variable with an
| expression, and produces no value.
| 

class ASSIGNMENT
    is_a STATEMENT

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | The target variable on the notional left-hand side of this assignment.
    | 
    prop target: VARIABLE_DECLARATION;

    | 
    | Source right hand side) of the assignment.
    | 
    prop source: EXPR_VALUE;


end
